#

Truffle Mushroom Risotto with Asparagus and Grilled Chicken

$25.99
680 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GourmetComfort FoodItalian

Description

A luxurious risotto infused with earthy truffle, complemented by tender grilled chicken and crisp asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Chicken breast: 2 pieces (6 oz each)
  • Fresh asparagus: 8 oz
  • Mushrooms (cremini or shiitake): 2 cups
  • Chicken broth: 4 cups
  • White wine: 1/2 cup
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Shallots: 1, minced
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
